{"tid":381001,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"3藍委場外禁食　小英派人送炸雞進議場","createTime":"2017-08-30T14:29:53.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-31T02:45:15.000Z","uid":53379,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f468726c9b58c25f07c5ae52e11637afe3930c06","tid":381001,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T14:29:53.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>3藍委場外禁食　小英派人送炸雞進議場</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n記者翁嫆琄／台北報導<br />\n<br />\n為了前瞻預算案，國民黨3名立委在立法院外禁食，但總統兼民進黨主席蔡英文30日下午派民進黨發言人吳沛憶、王閔生送炸雞、飲料到立院慰勞黨籍立委、助理們。民進黨團幹事長葉宜津說，他們絕對會在臨時會中通過前瞻預算及《國民體育法》，這些「主席的愛心」也會分送給國民黨、時代力量立委們。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.ettoday.net/images/2764/d2764620.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F2764%2Fd2764620.jpg&h=fb7f7150&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲吳沛憶、王閔生送炸雞、飲料到立院慰勞黨籍立委。（圖／記者翁嫆琄攝）<br />\n<br />\n國民黨立委費鴻泰、賴士葆、曾銘宗自昨晚起在立法院外禁食抗議，預定到臨時會結束為止，不過，立法院議場內倒是點心、飲料不斷，除了民進黨立委們都各自己來家鄉名產分享給大家外，國民黨立委們也帶冰品等點心享用。<br />\n<br />\n而吳沛憶、王閔生下午帶來蔡英文的愛心，共運送約100塊炸雞及飲料到立法院，準備分送給立委及助理們。<br />\n<br />\n出來接收慰勞品的葉宜津表示，他們絕對使命必達，會在臨時會中將前瞻預算、《國民體育法》修正案都順利審完，有這樣的決心可達成任務。<br />\n<br />\n▼國民黨立委們吃點心。（圖／記者翁嫆琄攝）<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.ettoday.net/images/2764/d2764874.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F2764%2Fd2764874.jpg&h=2b6b0a56&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://static.ettoday.net/images/2764/d2764619.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F2764%2Fd2764619.jpg&h=ddbd56be&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n至於會不會分享蔡英文的愛心給國民黨同仁？葉宜津立即說，「當然會」，民進黨的同仁讓人感動，常給她鼓勵，每個委員都在想自己選區有什麼好吃的名產，不但帶來慰勞大家，當然也跟國民黨分享，即使有時會被拒絕，但有時國民黨立委也會樂於分享。<br />\n<br />\n不過，對於會不會把這些分享給在場外禁食的立委們，葉宜津笑說，這樣對他們太不尊重了，但會想盡快審完，畢竟也是捨不得禁食的人，趕快審完他們也能趕快結束禁食。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.ettoday.net/images/2764/d2764621.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F2764%2Fd2764621.jpg&h=37d571ce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.ettoday.net/news/20170830/1000641.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F20170830%2F1000641.htm&d=j0gquRnbisANq9VFP9iEZwRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=2e5ad3b7\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.ettoday.net/news/20170830/1000641.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf1ccccc0d143f2132b45c4123cb687f3e135f00","tid":381001,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T14:34:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f673b9faa6c3d18906b7ad4d12b4775fb5fdff42","tid":381001,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T14:46:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef3dfdec871447a1b5b04ae0df059ab13e2424c5","tid":381001,"uid":5220,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T15:21:24.000Z","msg":"撚狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65a65ded30a102dbc7372dc6525f64a5ac62bac9","tid":381001,"uid":40979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T15:24:53.000Z","msg":"炸雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e375fc809baac9e5537fb3e5e537a5f02f8d318d","tid":381001,"uid":61748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T15:27:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ac32d9e97760c822bfd2adc22404b6264436560c","tid":381001,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T15:30:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>炸雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n加營多撈面<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquo